Battery --> RenewableEnergy
PowerSource <|.. PowerGrid
PowerSource <|.. Battery
PowerConsumer <|.. Battery
PowerConsumer <|.. PowerGrid
PowerConsumer <|-- HouseholdAppliance

RenewableEnergy <|.. SolarPower
